properties.name: Do You Have Rock n Roll?
properties.description:
All I could think of when I look at this week's route is that it looks an awful lot like the Leningrad Cowboys' haircut.

Which was in no way intentional, nor does it have any special meaning, really. But can we, like them , seek adventure and opportunity as we travel across the landscape? And, further, can we embody some of their innocence and naiveté, behold what we encounter with fresh eyes, perhaps creatively misunderstanding things a little? Yeah, we probably can. We are bikes in a city of cars. We're the weirdos out there rolling down the street (if not quite rocking). We have the silly hair, so to speak.

"Have you ever heard of 'rock n roll'? ...Study this book."
